          "It is consumed by init_game_from_capture(), build_map_from_capture(), solve_sequential(), zig_ffi._capture_to_map_args(), and solution_store.save_capture(). Each creator populates slightly different keys: iterate_local includes 'spawn', live_solver does not. Some include 'difficulty', some do not.",
