          "This pattern also exists in iterate_local.py, production_run.py, and several other scripts"
        ],
        "suggestion": "Wrap the argparse and module-level logic in an 'if __name__ == \"__main__\"' guard. This allows the optimization logic to be imported and called programmatically.",
